<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.8202960>
    dc:description "FIGURE 4. Hyalella carsone sp. nov., municipality of Bocaina do Sul, state of Santa Catarina (27°44′4.4″S 49°59′1.0″W). Paratype male, 6.75 mm, CCUFLA 449. (A) Gnathopod 1. (A1) Detail of carpus. (A2) Detail of propodus and dactylus. (B) Gnathopod 2. (B1) Detail of carpus. (B2) Detail of propodus and dactylus. Scale bars: A and B—0.4mm; A1 and A2—0.1 mm; B1 and B2—0.2 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/8202960/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.8202962>
    dc:description "FIGURE 5. Hyalella carsone sp. nov., municipality of Bocaina do Sul, state of Santa Catarina (27°44′4.4″S 49°59′1.0″W). Paratype male, 6.75 mm, CCUFLA 449. (A) Pereopod 3. (B) Pereopod 4. (C) Pereopod 5. (D) Pereopod 6. (E) Pereopod 7. Scale bars: 0.4 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/8202962/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.8202958>
    dc:description "FIGURE 3. Hyalella carsone sp. nov., municipality of Bocaina do Sul, state of Santa Catarina (27°44′4.4″S 49°59′1.0″W). Paratype male, 6.75 mm, CCUFLA 449. (A) Antenna 1. (B) Antenna 2. (C) Left mandible. (D) Right mandible. (E) Lower lip. (F) Upper lip. (G) Maxilla 1. (H) Maxilla 2. (I) Maxilliped. (I1) Detail of article 4, article 3 and nail of maxilliped. Scale bars, A, B, C and I1—0.4 mm; D to I—0.2 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/8202958/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.8202971>
    dc:description "FIGURE 9. Hyalella wangarie sp. nov., municipality of Campos Novos, state of Santa Catarina (27°19′29″S 51°12′28″W). (A) Holotype male, 6.62 mm, MZUSP 44142. (B) Paratype, female, 7.65 mm. Scale Bars: 1 mm. Photograph: G. O. Reis." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/8202971/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.8202968>
    dc:description "FIGURE 8. Schematic plate. (A) Aesthetascs present on antenna 1 of Hyalella carsone sp. nov. (B) Aesthetascs present on antenna 1 of Hyalella wangarie sp. nov. (C) Schematic serrate seta subtype F3 based on Zimmer et al. (2009). (D) The new type of seta serrate with accessory seta." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/8202968/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.8202964>
    dc:description "FIGURE 6. Hyalella carsone sp. nov., municipality of Bocaina do Sul, state of Santa Catarina (27°44′4.4″S 49°59′1.0″W). Paratype male, 6.75 mm, CCUFLA 449. (A) Pleopod. (B) Uropod 1. (C) Uropod 2. (D) Uropod 3. (E) and (F) Telson. Scale bars: A and B—0.4 mm; C to F—0.2 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/8202964/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.8202956>
    dc:description "FIGURE 2.Hyalella carsone sp.nov., municipalityof Bocaina do Sul, state of Santa Catarina, Brazil(27°44′4.4″S49°59′1.0″W). (A) Holotype male, 7.35 mm, MZUSP 44141. (B) Paratype female, 6.38 mm. Scale bars: 1 mm. Author: G. O. Reis." ;
