<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.8202966>
    dc:description "FIGURE 7. Hyalella carsone sp. nov., municipality of Bocaina do Sul, state of Santa Catarina (27°44′4.4″S 49°59′1.0″W). Paratype female, 7.07 mm, CCUFLA 449. (A) Gnathopod 1. (B) Gnathopod 2. (C) and (D) Telson. Scale bars: A and B—0,4 mm; C and D—0.2 mm." ;
